text: Hippocamp or Hippocampus may refer to: ==Science== * Hippocampus, an anatomical subdivision of the brain, so named for its physical resemblance to a seahorse (genus Hippocampus) * Hippocampus (genus), the seahorse genus * Hippocampus (journal) * Hippocamp (moon), a moon of Neptune ==Mythology== * Hippocampus (mythology) or hippocamp, a mythological sea-horse ==Media== * Hippo Campus, an American indie rock band
